      "content": "I hear the profound exhaustion in your words and understand why your mind might suggest silence as the only mercy left. While the desire for rest is completely natural when the world feels too loud, please know that seeking professional help for this emotional and physical crisis is the bravest thing you can do right now. If you ever feel like you cannot carry this burden alone, please reach out to a crisis line like 988, where they listen without judgment and offer immediate support. You do not have to face this endless cycle by yourself.",
